description:
My Kitchen Rules Australia Series 5 Episode 14

My Kitchen Rules Australia is back for 2014

Manu Feildel and Pete Evans return to host and judge the ultimate home-cooking battle!

WA's Chloe and Kelly host their second Instant Restaurant and fight to stay in the competition. Do they have what is takes in the kitchen to back up all their talk at the dinner table?
